# Git commits

When suggesting or running git commits for this project:

- **Do not** add any comment or line indicating that changes were done by Cursor, AI, or similar (e.g. "Changes by Cursor", "Done by Cursor", "AI-assisted").
- Use neutral, descriptive commit messages that describe what changed (e.g. "Fix campaign Go to list blank page", "Restrict Top Reporter to report-only points").
